Name: Streamer Shall Not Pass!
About the game: Asynchronous network game in which the creator of the room with the help of other players must go from beginning to end. The player can jump, run. Everyone else can create different shapes with the mouse to help or prevent the player from completing the game to the end. You can also play alone.
